  "texts": [
    "This is particularly relevant when contrasting how one fits a GLM compared to an ensemble model.",
    "In particular, less attention is given to selecting features that are included in the model (e.g.",
    "using correlation as a filter), but rather the ensemble model decides on what features are given the most attention.",
    "This is further highlighted in deep learning, where layers in the neural network handle aspects of feature engineering.",
    "20 AI skills here refers to both the technical aspects required to develop, validate, and interpret AI systems/models and the skills required to ensure the ethical use of AI."
  ]
}